div.p: This pipeline is high level design for fetching exchange rates data from source to transforming the transactions data.

ol.li:
Schedule of refresh can be set to transform daily/ accordingly to avoid one time transformation at the end of the Financial Year
Any time when this transformed data is queried, it will always have transformed data i.e., transaction amount in different currencies till previous day

Scalability factor:
We are fetching currency exchange rate accordingly with base currrency "EUR"
At max in a day, total currencies we have in System (C) is the total number of records fetched per the run/ day as defined accordingly
Since, exchange rate data is available in base currency it reduces data (CxC) rows of data for conversion
